## Benchmarks

Tested on a simulated support agent (5 tasks, 10 runs each):

| Metric | Baseline | With RunCore | Change |
|--------|---------|-------------|--------|
| CpST | $0.00773 | $0.00060 | **−92%** |
| Total tokens | 2,402 | 2,020 | −16% |
| Duplicate calls blocked | — | 10 | — |
| Loop risk score | 0.41 | 0.03 | −93% |

